thread.title: Gordon Holliday

author: Gordon Holliday
title: Gordon Holliday
text: I was looking a various company packaging services online for my first custom boxes. The third website I came across was PACKLANE. And what first caught my eye is how the buyer can make a live custom box, various dimensions, and visualize it 3D. It baffled me, and made me want to purchase right away. Then the customer service experience was very helpful, and timely when I ordered from them! I will definitely be using PACKLANE again and again!
